      "amount": "a pinch"
    },
    {
      "name": "Coriander seeds",
      "amount": "a pinch"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a pan over medium heat.",
    "Add onion and garlic, sauté until softened. Add thyme leaves, cumin seeds, and coriander seeds; cook for another minute.",
    "Gently add courgettes to the pan and stir-fry for about 5 minutes or until they start to soften slightly.",
    "Pour in tomato paste and allow it to cook until it thickens slightly. Reduce heat to low and cover the pan with a lid, allowing the courgettes to poach gently for around 10 minutes.",
    "Serve hot as a light meal."
  ],
